      "title": "Policy-as-Versioned-Flux — live cloud-plane compliance (issue 21, C2P result2oscal)",
      "last-modified": "2026-07-15T00:00:00+00:00",
      "version": "1.0",
      "oscal-version": "1.1.2",
      "remarks": "Production component-definition for the CronJob (infrastructure/c2p/), not a spike. Maps the two real cloud-plane ValidatingPolicies to their real NIST 800-53r5 controls -- sc-28 (protection of information at rest), cp-10 (information system recovery and reconstitution). The workload plane deliberately carries no NIST mapping (internal governance, not security controls) -- see policy repo's rationale docs."
    },
